{
  "stem": "3331.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then later, when, when, when I was in the AK, my brother, with a few-- there were-- there were left only about 15 from the 125.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were killed and killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how long did it take, till the end of the war, from that point?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then the war-- I was liberated-- then I came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, from the AK, there was a other killing, which I don't want to go in in it, because I-- the commandant gave out the order to go and kill three Jews, and I volunteered as a volunteer to go and kill them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in the AK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted to go there, because on the way, I killed my-- the man, and I came, and I took out the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they survived the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't go back to my group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were hiding--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--by a peasant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the man who came, who belonged to our group, was from this village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came-- he was home for the weekend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And he came, and he said, that-- I know Jews are being hidden.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Please, can you go and tell her--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went, and I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I volunteered, I couldn't go back to my group anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And then the night-- the 28 to 29th of July, we were liberated by the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were a-- what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First, I didn't believe-- yeah, well, the, the night-- I have to tell you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The night that I was liberated, the night I was lib-- how much do-- how much time do we have?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The night that I was liberated-- the last night-- I was running from our group, which was in German hands.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
